    "# BoxCar Ridesharing Simulation — Squareshire\n",
    "## Discrete-Event Simulation Study\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook implements a full discrete-event simulation of the BoxCar ridesharing system operating in Squareshire (a 20×20 mile square region). It covers:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Input Data Analysis** — Examining the provided driver and rider datasets to calibrate parameters\n",
    "2. **Simulation Model** — A heap-based DES engine with all spec-required features\n",
    "3. **Baseline vs Calibrated Scenarios** — Comparing BoxCar's assumed parameters against data-driven ones\n",
    "4. **Improvement Proposals** — Testing interventions including an adaptive ellipse-ring repositioning policy\n",
    "5. **Statistical Inference** — 95% confidence intervals and pairwise Welch t-tests"
   ]
  },
