    "---\n",
    "# Statistics\n",
    "\n",
    "We do some statistics now in order to compare results. We use a Welch test to do tests from wto samples with unequal variances."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "d8693e4b",
   "metadata": {},
